            "body": "Cool, thanks\n\nFor reference:\nI had this to automatically open the quickfix window once it has been populated with a quickfix command (such as `cgetexpr`):\n`au QuickFixCmdPost [^l]* cwindow`\n\nI now made it `au QuickFixCmdPost [^l]* botright cwindow`. This seems to give me the expected behaviour no matter how I split my windows, even if I don't split them at all.\n",
